vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of a street easement to SEVA, Ltd., the abutting owner, containing approximately 443 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Cockrell Hill Road and Interstate Highway 30; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Fund $6,645.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
